title: onedin line season 8 at last! ripped from tv
description:
AT LAST the Onedin Line series 8, which the BBC stubbornly refuses to release on DVD or even VHS, is available to the world. The files are .avi and are reasonable sound and picture quality considering they were saved from VHS recordings from the telly. You must expect a little bit of warbling on the sound and some fuzzy lines and video glitches, but nothing that spoils the enjoyment of the show!

This is the last series of this show, please keep seeding after I am finished as I will have other stuff to upload and will not have the bandwidth. All Enjoy!
